Install Debian on MicroSD: https://github.com/ayufan-rock64/linux-build/releases/download/0.7.8/stretch-minimal-rock64-0.7.8-1061-arm64.img.xz

Username: rock64
Password: rock64

sudo su

Run prep as normal.

Build: /root/nems/nems-admin/nems-build.sh 1.4.1 45

Set the timezone: dpkg-reconfigure tzdata

Fix the time: wget -O - https://www.baldnerd.com/nerdgasms/linuxdate/ajax.php?tz=192 | { read gmt; date -s "$gmt"; }

Edit /etc/locale.gen and uncomment en_CA.UTF-8 UTF-8

Run locale-gen

Reboot

Cleanup
